summary:
My professional career is described by 10 years in client assistance and 3 years in sales of international services & marketing research and since September 2021 I began a new challenge in logistics. 
I'm Romanian native speaker, Italian C1 speaker and English B2 speaker.

Regarding my life journey:
I'm born in Romania where I lived until I turned 23 and after I graduated the university on 2003, I relocated in Italy were I'm living since 20 years and I achieved the Italian citizenship.

I'm always open for new challenges, new cultures, new life experiences that can enrich myself and my professional career .

Open to relocation in EU
